High Level Requirements:

  ID	                    Description
HL_01	      Convert Text to Speech Accurately
HL_02     	Convert Speech to Text Accurately
HL_03	      Recognize the voice accurately
HL_04     	Play the sounds according to the keypad names
HL_05     	Redirect to the call page when user click on call page
HL_06	      Sound should not play according to keypad names while we switch off  the button


Low level requirements:

  ID	                      Description
LL_01	     Android mobile with Chrome 
LL_02	     Minimum 3MB is required to download 
LL_03	     Display the message while speech to text conversion
LL_04   	 Display the Try Again message when user does not speak or unable to recognize the speech

